item.title: CVE-2024-33000|2024-05-14T04:02:46.636Z -- SAP_SE -- SAP Bank Account Management
item.description: SAP Bank Account Management does not perform necessary authorization check for an authorized user, resulting in escalation of privileges. As a result, it has a low impact to confidentiality to the system.
